# Group 4 Project for CPSC 441, Fall 2020


### System Setup
```{r}
install.packages('tidytuesdayR')
library(tidytuesdayR)
tt_datasets(2018)
tt_datasets(2019)
tt_datasets(2020)

malaria = tt_load(2018, 33)
malaria_cases = malaria$malaria_inc
malaria_age = malaria$malaria_deaths_age
malaria_deaths = malaria$malaria_deaths
voter = tt_load(2018,28)
voter_data = voter$voter_turnout



```
